{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Australia{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Yes. And our - and him and my mother both went out to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Australia{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} because my sister had gone out to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Australia{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} with a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6444694\charrsid13305173 cousin}{
