\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11886869 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 Do you know if she worked before she got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14761640 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 Well - yes, she worked -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11886869 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 She worked at the Tweed Mill?
