\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14761640 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 No. Not afterwards. No she didn't go out to work after she got married. And - I was trying to think of something that happened -
