No, they had to go down to the mill and they still have to go down there now to do the work there and - and the conditions of the working was rather different to what it is today }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3760673\charrsid13305173 down}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173  there. And - you'd go down - perhaps one of the streets, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}New Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 for instance, and - you'd see a lot the people coming away from the work and if you go down today and see them coming away you see the vast difference in the cleanliness of the person. They used to come out v
ery dirty and - some of them looked a bit bedraggled and - vastly }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3760673\charrsid13305173 different}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 
 to what they do today. And they ladies when they come out today from their looms, they look quite spick and span. There's all that difference.
