 returned to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14761640 EB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14306447\charrsid13305173 Oh - Rockhill - Rockhill, yes.
